== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
《獵巫行動：大滅絕》最初計劃在2012年推出，並由[[提默·貝克曼比托夫|提默·貝克曼比托夫]]基於柯里·古德曼的劇本來執導<ref>{{cite web|last=Foreman|first=Liza|title=Vin Diesel in Talks for Summit's 'The Last Witch Hunter'|url=http://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/vin-diesel-talks-summits-last-witch-hunter-exclusive-55156|publisher=The Wrap|accessdate=2014-04-06|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521221052/https://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/vin-diesel-talks-summits-last-witch-hunter-exclusive-55156/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，貝克曼比托夫被換成了[[布雷克·艾斯納|布雷克·艾斯納]]，而古德曼的劇本則被D·W·哈珀和[[梅麗莎·沃雷克|梅麗莎·沃雷克]]重新改寫<ref name=STYD>{{cite web|last=Turek|first=Ryan|title=Dallas Buyers Club Scribe Boards The Last Witch Hunter|url=http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/351031-dallas-buyers-club-scribe-boards-the-last-witch-hunter/|publisher=STYD|accessdate=2014-04-06|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081019/http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/351031-dallas-buyers-club-scribe-boards-the-last-witch-hunter/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=SR>{{cite web|last=Taormina|first=Anthony|title=Vin Diesel In Talks for Summit's 'Last Witch Hunter'|url=http://screenrant.com/vin-diesel-last-witch-hunter/|publisher=Screen Rant|accessdate=2014-04-06|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162100/https://screenrant.com/vin-diesel-last-witch-hunter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。接著，宣布[[馮·迪索|馮·迪索]]將出演本片，並由[[獅門影業|獅門影業]]製作和發行<ref name=STYD />。電影在[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]申請了1400萬美元的稅收抵免<ref>{{cite web|last=Schooley|first=Tim|title=Exclusive: Vin Diesel movie may shoot in Pittsburgh|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/pittsburgh/news/2013/09/30/vin-diesel-movie-may-shoot-in-pittsburgh.html?page=all|publisher=Biz Journals|accessdate=2014-04-06|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123014554/https://www.bizjournals.com/pittsburgh/news/2013/09/30/vin-diesel-movie-may-shoot-in-pittsburgh.html?page=all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Schooley|first=Tim|title=Film industry hoping to recoup more than $22 million in tax credits|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/pittsburgh/news/2014/05/13/film-industry-hoping-to-recoup-more-than-22.html?page=all|publisher=Pittsburgh Business Times|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123010702/https://www.bizjournals.com/pittsburgh/news/2014/05/13/film-industry-hoping-to-recoup-more-than-22.html?page=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年2月，迪索在他的[[Facebook|Facebook]]上發布了電影的概念藝術，此外，獅門影業的首席執行官喬·菲茨梅爾表示，如果電影能成功，那《獵巫行動：大滅絕》將有可能發展成一個系列<ref>{{cite web|last=Terrero|first=Nina|title=Vin Diesel reveals 'Last Witch Hunter' artwork sneak peek -- PHOTO|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/02/20/vin-diesel-ast-witch-hunter-photo/|publisher=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2014-04-06|archive-date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027060532/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/02/20/vin-diesel-ast-witch-hunter-photo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年7月，官方宣布[[蘿絲·萊斯莉|蘿絲·萊斯莉]]將加入劇組與迪索共同出演<ref>{{cite news|title='Game of Thrones' Actress Joins Vin Diesel in 'The Last Witch Hunter'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/game-thrones-actress-joins-vin-718066|accessdate=2014-07-12|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-07-11|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612184508/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/game-thrones-actress-joins-vin-718066|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於同年8月，[[伊利亞·伍德|伊利亞·伍德]]、[[米高·肯恩|米高·肯恩]]與[[奧拉維爾·達里·拉夫森|奧拉維爾·達里·拉夫森]]也被宣布參演本片<ref>{{cite web|last1=Yamato|first1=Jen|script-title=en:Elijah Wood Joins ‘The Last Witch Hunter’|url=http://deadline.com/2014/08/elijah-wood-last-witch-hunter-vin-diesel-814293/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=2014-08-14|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211205108/https://deadline.com/2014/08/elijah-wood-last-witch-hunter-vin-diesel-814293/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|script-title=en:Michael Caine Joins Vin Diesel’s ‘The Last Witch Hunter’|url=http://deadline.com/2014/07/michael-caine-last-witch-hunter-casting-vin-diesel-807217/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=2014-08-14|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122105440/https://deadline.com/2014/07/michael-caine-last-witch-hunter-casting-vin-diesel-807217/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=ÓLAFSDÓTTIR KAABER|first1=EMILÍA S.|script-title=en:Ólafur Darri Cast in ‘The Last Witch Hunter’|url=http://icelandreview.com/news/2014/08/10/olafur-darri-cast-last-witch-hunter|publisher=Iceland Review|accessdate=2014-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814125945/http://icelandreview.com/news/2014/08/10/olafur-darri-cast-last-witch-hunter|archive-date=2014-08-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[茱莉·恩格爾布雷希特|茱莉·恩格爾布雷希特]]和[[洛特·弗貝克|洛特·弗貝克]]也將加盟劇組<ref>{{cite news|script-title=en:German Actress Julie Engelbrecht Joins ‘The Last Witch Hunter’|url=http://deadline.com/2014/09/last-witch-hunter-julie-engelbrecht-828137/|publisher=deadline.com|accessdate=2015-06-18|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126111031/https://deadline.com/2014/09/last-witch-hunter-julie-engelbrecht-828137/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=First still shot with Vin Diesel on The Last Witch Hunter. So excited!|url=https://twitter.com/lotteverbeek1/status/520786841650622464|publisher=Lotte Verbeek|accessdate=2014-10-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304111202/https://twitter.com/lotteverbeek1/status/520786841650622464|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年2月，[[史蒂夫·賈布隆斯基|史蒂夫·賈布隆斯基]]被聘為電影作曲。

