== 續集 ==
2015年6月17日，迪索在自己的Facebook上證實了續集的發展，並指出片商已想發展出《獵巫行動》系列，並要他計畫好續集的時間<ref>{{cite web|title=Vin Diesel on Facebook|url=https://www.facebook.com/VinDiesel/photos/a.101465923312.101581.89562268312/10153500958638313/?type=1&theater|publisher=facebook.com|accessdate=2015-06-22|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308083330/https://www.facebook.com/VinDiesel/photos/a.101465923312.101581.89562268312/10153500958638313/?type=1&theater|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=Vin Diesel Says The Last Witch Hunter Sequel Already in Development|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/451273-vin-diesel-says-the-last-witch-hunter-sequel-already-in-development|accessdate=2015-06-22|work=comingsoon.net|date=2015-06-17|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123053214/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/451273-vin-diesel-says-the-last-witch-hunter-sequel-already-in-development|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但因本片的口碑不佳和迪索忙於其他電影，使得續集發展的可行性渺茫<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Vin-Diesel-Drops-Details-Next-Riddick-Movie-Get-Them-Here-100617.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-12-24 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305181858/https://www.cinemablend.com/new/Vin-Diesel-Drops-Details-Next-Riddick-Movie-Get-Them-Here-100617.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

